branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
Series MGQ is a compact body actuator integrated with internal guide shafts to isolate the load bearing from the movement of the actuator&apos;s rod and seals. The MGQM carbon steel alloy slide bearing variant provides lateral stability protecting it from side load impacts.The MGQL high precision ball bushing variant allows for smooth operation that ensures stable travel resistance.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchItem.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The MGQM is a compact body actuator integrated with internal guide shafts to isolate the load bearing from the movement of the actuator&apos;s rod and seals. The carbon steel alloy slide bearing provides lateral stability protecting it from side load impacts. Non-rotating accuracy ranging from +/-0.04&#xb0; for 100 mm bore to +/-0.08&#xb0; for 12 mm bore.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchItem.bullets:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bore sizes: 12, 16, 20, 25, 32, 40, 50, 63, 80, 100 mm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High temperature option, up to 150&amp;deg;C or 302&amp;deg;F (XB6)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Rubber bumpers as standard&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Auto switch capable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

branchItem.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The MGQL is a compact body actuator integrated with internal guide shafts to isolate the load bearing from the movement of the actuator&apos;s rod and seals. The high precision ball bushing allows for smooth operation that ensures stable travel resistance. Non-rotating accuracy ranging from +/-0.05&#xb0; for 100 mm bore to +/-0.10&#xb0; for 12 mm bore.
&lt;/p&gt;

